                                nature education programmes in India. Alongside NEAF, I also contribute to developing
                                nature learning resources and support other ongoing work. I hope to continue learning
                                and contribute towards Nature Classrooms’ efforts to make nature learning more
                                accessible within classroom spaces.</p>
